{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_305","type":"agent_message","text":"The mobile form looks good, but the desktop form screenshot exposed a real layout problem: inside the workspace canvas, the audio settings fields are cramming into two columns and overlapping. I’m inspecting the shared form-column breakpoint now and will patch the audio stage so it falls back to a single readable column in that narrower canvas width."}}
