{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_337","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented prompt 70 end to end. The app now has durable session-level audio settings on the backend, a dedicated audio-stage editor in the workspace, persisted chat/action echoes for audio changes, hydrated resume support, and story-tool defaults that reuse the saved audio plan for later narration runs. I also fixed a desktop layout issue found during live browser QA by forcing the audio form to a single readable column inside the workspace editor pane.\n\nVerification is complete:\n- `make backend-lint` passed.\n- `make backend-test` passed with `241 passed, 5 skipped`.\n- `make frontend-test` passed with `105 passed`.\n- `make frontend-build` passed.\n- `cd backend && python -m pytest tests/test_migrations.py -q` passed.\n- Live browser QA passed against the Docker Compose stack after applying `alembic upgrade head` to the persisted local Postgres volume.\n- Screenshots were captured at [audio-settings-desktop.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/tools/webapp-qa/.artifacts/prompt-70/audio-settings-desktop.png), [audio-settings-mobile.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/tools/webapp-qa/.artifacts/prompt-70/audio-settings-mobile.png), [audio-settings-desktop-form.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/tools/webapp-qa/.artifacts/prompt-70/audio-settings-desktop-form.png), and [audio-settings-mobile-form.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/tools/webapp-qa/.artifacts/prompt-70/audio-settings-mobile-form.png).\n\nCheckpoint commits:\n- `79724eb feat(prompt-70): add durable audio settings stage`\n- `bd0d96a fix(prompt-70): tighten audio settings QA and migration`\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/70_audio_settings_model_and_ui/summary.md)."}}
